  "steps": [
    "●Get plates, aspirate media",
    "●Add 2mL ice cold DPBS",
    "○Aspirate DPBS",
    "●Add 500uL Trizol/well in chemical hood",
    "●Bring yellow tubes to hood, collect trizol and add to tubes",
    "●Add 100uL chloroform to tubes",
    "○hand shake 15s",
    "○Place on ice 5min until see layers (aq/lipids/bottom)",
    "●Spin full speed 20min cold centrifuge",
    "○During, make 70% ethanol on ice (3mL RNAse-free water + 7mL ethanol)",
    "○Make new ep set 1-9",
    "●In hood, collect top layer after spinning and place into eppendorfs",
    "○**take note of first volume and make all the same",
    "○Mix 1:1 ethanol with supernatant, use same tip to transfer from eppendorfs into pink spin tubes",
    "●Spin 9000x 1min bench centrifuge",
    "○Discard flowthrough in hood, keep tube",
    "●Add 350uL RW1 buffer to tubes",
    "○Spin 1 min",
    "○During, prepare DNAse soln (with syringe)",
    "●Add 70uL DNAse soln to middle of each column, leave 15min RT",
    "●Repeat RW1 and spin",
    "○Discard collection tube and get new",
    "●Wash RPE 500uL",
    "○Spin 1min",
    "○Discard collection and keep tubes",
    "●Repeat RPE, spin 2min",
    "○Discard tubes",
    "●Spin 1min empty to dry",
    "○Get new eppendorfs, label",
    "●Place pink tubes on top of eppendorfs",
    "●Add 30uL RNAse free water, centrifuge 1min",
    "○Close tubes as quickly as possible and keep on ice→ nanodrop"
  ],
